      "description": "Trigger: The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} is [[lookup @activation.condition activity=9T8cNbSBVACrrmRI]].\n\nResponse: The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} reduces the damage it takes from the attack by [[/healing average]], and if that damage is reduced to 0, the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can redirect some of the attack's force.\n\nDexterity Saving Throw: DC [[lookup @save.dc.value activity=x0MjUmnv2OPAbm6y]], one [[lookup @target.affects.type activity=x0MjUmnv2OPAbm6y]] the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can see within [[lookup @range.value activity=x0MjUmnv2OPAbm6y]] feet.\n\nFailure: [[/damage average]] damage.",
